sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant G as Gateway
    participant A as Go 接入服务
    participant R as Redis
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant C as 订单消费者
    participant P as PostgreSQL

    U->>G: POST /seckill<br/>request_id
    G->>G: 鉴权、资格、限流、防重放
    G->>A: 转发请求
    A->>R: EVAL 预占 Lua
    R->>R: 检查 request_id
    R->>R: 检查一人一单
    R->>R: 领取库存令牌
    R->>R: 写 reservation
    R-->>A: RESERVED + reservation_id

    A->>M: CreateOrderMessage
    alt 发送已确认
        M-->>A: ACK
        A->>R: RESERVED -> PUBLISHED
    else 发送超时或结果未知
        A->>R: 保持 RESERVED/标记 RECONCILING
    end

    A-->>U: QUEUED

    M->>C: 投递消息
    C->>P: 开启本地事务
    C->>P: 插入 Inbox
    C->>P: 领取库存令牌
    C->>P: 创建订单
    C->>P: 写库存流水和 Outbox
    C->>P: COMMIT
    C-->>M: ACK

    C->>R: 更新 ORDERED，或由 Outbox 异步更新
    U->>R: 查询最终状态
    R-->>U: ORDER_CREATED
